==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Catch-basin
<hw>Catch"-ba`sin</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A cistern or
vault at the point where a street gutter discharges into a sewer, to
catch bulky matters which would not pass readily through the
sewer.</def> <rj><au>Knight.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Catch crop</ent>⟦br⟧
